Young trans people discuss sexuality, sex and relationships – podcast



This podcast is tied to a week-long Generation Y takeover in G2 and online – particularly Wednesday's sex issue. This discussion was organised in collaboration with All About Trans, an outreach project aimed at improving trans representation in the media.

This podcast contains strong language and frank discussion throughout. Reading on mobile? Click here to listen

